          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1684495808278-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim, then slice the <strong>spring onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Slice the<strong> red chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> finely</p><p>Dice the <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</strong> </span>finely</p>",
